<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="section-label">FAQs</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Common Questions <span class="heading-gradient">About Tak2ai</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Everything you need to know before getting started.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-accordion animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">What is Tak2ai and how does it work?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Tak2ai is an AI automation platform that helps businesses handle voice calls and chats automatically. You tell us what you need, we set up the AI with your scripts and data, and it starts working — calling leads and answering messages without human involvement.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">Which services does Tak2ai offer?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Tak2ai offers AI Voice Calling with Indian virtual numbers and intelligent AI Chatbots with a ChatGPT-like interface you can embed anywhere.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">How quickly can I get started?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most businesses go live within 2-5 days. Simple WhatsApp bot setups can be ready in under 48 hours. Voice AI systems typically take 3-5 days including script setup and testing. Video generation starts working immediately after onboarding.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">Do I need technical skills to use it?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>No. We handle all the technical setup including AI training, script configuration, and integrations. You just provide your requirements and we take care of the rest. A simple dashboard lets you monitor performance and tweak settings anytime.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">What languages does Tak2ai support?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Tak2ai supports Hindi, English, Bengali, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Marathi, Gujarati, and more. Our AI understands and responds naturally in the language your customers prefer, including Hinglish code-mixing common in Indian conversations.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">Is my data safe and secure?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely. All data is encrypted in transit and at rest. We host on Indian servers compliant with local data residency requirements. We never share or sell your data. Custom NDAs and enterprise security agreements are available on request.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark section-contained">
